 20 万元；赔偿姚策精神损害抚慰金 20 万元；河南大学淮河医院赔偿姚策各项费用共计 361312.94 元（已给付 10 万元，尚需给付 261312.94 元）。 2021 年 2 月 8 日下午，「错换人生 28 年」案于河南省开封市中级人民法院二审宣判。法院对于郭希宽、杜新枝、姚策的上诉不予支持，维持开封市鼓楼区人民法院一审原判，赔偿郭希宽、杜新枝精神损害抚慰金 20 万元，赔偿姚策精神损害抚慰金 20 万元。对于姚策的上诉请求予以支持，河南大学淮河医院赔偿姚策医疗费、营养费、误工费、交通费等各项费用共计 60 余万元。2 月 24 日，姚策生母是否故意偷换孩子，话题在网络上掀起热议。对此，姚策生母表示，作为一个母亲，自己是绝对不会有这种想法的。3 月 18 日，有媒体报道，姚策已进入安宁疗护阶段，癌细胞扩散至肺部、淋巴、骨头等全身各处，已无治疗方案，靠输营养液维持生命。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d5a22a3611ea5e10f271a97665f45ce_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "101 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/450843427"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+v6f7YLm3ZsBEAMaCDYyNDY2NDQ3IJSz5oIGMGk4uCZAJnIJNDUwODQzNDI3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1616595013.974492", "card_id": "Q_448235022", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "基金一直下滑，现在卖掉行不行？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8c53f2b418d6679042a26b4836ca9bd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/448235022"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I+v6f7YLm3ZsBEAMaCDYxODg2NzI1IPmLl4IGMAA4a0Ancgk0NDgyMzUwMjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1616595013.974803", "card_id": "Q_449660986", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 118}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么有些人明明具有天赋，却没有取得相应的成就？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ae30021ebff66e0e4807b15af9bd51e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/449660986"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+v6f7YLm3